casebody.data:
No. 10-1107. Charles L. Ryan, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections, Petitioner v. David S. Detrich. 563 U.S. 984, 131 S. Ct. 2449,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1206,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3694. May 16, 2011.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Cullen v. Pinhol-ster, 563 U.S. 170, 131 S. Ct. 1388, 179 L. Ed. 2d 557 (2011).

Same case below, 619 F.3d 1038.
